     $(function () {

                    loadGallery(galleries, "#galleryHolder");

                    loadBannerGallery(bannerGallery, ".homeBannerGallery");

                });



                /*-- homeGallery: START */
                function loadGallery(gals, selector) {
                    if (gals[0].items.length) {
                        $.map(gals, function (gallery) {
                            for (var i = 0; i < gallery.items.length; ++i) {
                                var it;
                                var item = gallery.items[i];
                                if (item) {
                                    it = "<img src='" + item.img + "' alt='img1' />";
                                    $(selector).append(it);
                                }
                            }
                        });
                        $(selector).jqFancyTransitions({ width: 942, height: 495, effect: "fade", delay: 9000 });
                    }
                }

                /*-- homeGallery: END */

                /*-- BannerGallery: START */
                function loadBannerGallery(gals, selector) {
                    var Pos1HasBanners = false;
                    var Pos2HasBanners = false;
                    if (gals[0].items.length > 0) {
                        $.map(gals, function (gallery) {
                            for (var i = 0; i < gallery.items.length; ++i) {

                                var it;
                                var item = gallery.items[i];

                                if (item) {
                                    it = "<div class='item'><div class='row1'>" + item.row1 + "</div><div class='row2'>" + item.row2 + "</div>";
                                    it += "<a href='" + item.url + "' target='" + item.target + "'><img class='bannerImg' src='" + item.img + "' border='0' alt='' /></a></div>";
                                    if (item.pos == "1") {
                                        $(selector).find('.banners1 .itemMover').append(it);
                                        Pos1HasBanners = true;
                                    } else if (item.pos == "2") {
                                        $(selector).find('.banners2 .itemMover').append(it);
                                        Pos2HasBanners = true;
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        });
                    }
                    setBannerGallery();
                    if (!Pos1HasBanners) {
                        $('.banners1').hide();
                    }
                    if (!Pos2HasBanners) {
                        $('.banners2').hide();
                    }
                }

                /*-- BannerGallery: END */

                function showHideTab() {
                    $('.homeMovableTabArrow').css('display', 'none');
                    if ($('#movableTab').hasClass('active')) {
                        $('#movableTab').animate({
                            left: '-=110px'
                        }, 500,
                        function () {
                            $(this).removeClass('active');
                            $('.homeMovableTabArrow').css('display', 'block');
                        });
                    } else {
                        $('#movableTab').animate({
                            left: '+=110px'
                        }, 500,
                        function () {
                            $(this).addClass('active');
                            $('.homeMovableTabArrow').css('display', 'block');
                        });
                    }
                }
    </script>
